textAfterTable: 11 Songs Customer Reviews Soothing yet exciting           by Duckybuddha I guess like most I've found RJ via Soundcloud and was excited to hear of his new release. This album is great from start to finish and it ranges from subtle piano pieces to electronic upbeat tracks. It's actually hard to pigeonhole but if you want to be lost in an amazing variety of cinematic sounds, give it a go, you won't be disappointed. 5 stars           by Diamondelite49 WOW, I love this album!
